<hw>U"le</hw> <pr>(⟦umac⟧"l⟦esl⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Sp.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A Mexican and Central American tree
(<spn>Castilloa elastica</spn> and <spn>Castilloa Markhamiana</spn>)
related to the breadfruit tree. Its milky juice contains
<prod>caoutchouc</prod>. Called also <altname>ule
tree</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
